RAM Security (Anti-PC Crash): The launcher now uses the native Node.js OS module to detect the user's total physical RAM. It automatically sets the maximum limit of the cursors while always keeping 2 GB of margin for Windows. (No more crashes because a player has added 16 GB of RAM when he only has 8!).

Persistent Logs System: The launcher creates a logs folder in AppData. Each launch generates a text file (launcher_date.log). It intelligently only keeps the last 5 files so as not to pollute the hard drive.

Console Ergonomics: * I added a "Copy" button in the console so that the user can send you their logs in one click.

If the game stops with an error code (Crash), the console automatically opens on the screen so that the user understands that there was a problem.


